# =============================================================================
# DeskAgent .gitignore - public repo (deskagent-ai/community)
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Secrets - NEVER commit these
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Note: deskagent/config/*.json are SYSTEM DEFAULTS / TEMPLATES with placeholder
# values like "YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY" or empty strings. They MUST be committed
# so OSS users see the expected structure. Real user values live in the
# user-override config directory ($PROJECT_DIR/config/, outside deskagent/),
# which is never part of this repo at all.
#
# We only ignore artifacts that should never appear here:
# hardware-bound binary license
config/license.dat
# encrypted user-config output
config/encrypted_*.json
# opt-in convention for local overrides
config/*.local.json

